![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/a77b98b5-ebd3-4233-835d-fd96ce385e37/PhotoGrid_1_20240621170644.jpg)

CM Punk returns to Chicago and they welcome him with an enormous reaction.

CM Punk is talking about how he wanted to bury Drew McIntyre's career. When Paul Heyman inturrupts.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/518bb069-c94c-4f17-8a19-28749746f777/20240621_171750.jpg)

Paul Heyman tells CM Punk that he has to leave or the Bloodline is going to jump him.

CM Punk laughs at the idea but Solo comes out. Solo asks Punk to acknowledge him and Punk raises the finger.

Punk says he acknowledges… that he doesn’t see the Bloodline in front of him. Just a couple of fake Usos and a costly Tribal Cheif.

The Bloodline is going to jump Punk but Cody Rhodes comes out with two baseball bats. The ring is cleared and Cody challenged Solo for a match TONIGHT!!

