![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/577d4a0f-3cfe-4e8d-8810-a92a6e22f2e7/20240621_181728.jpg)

LA Knight calls out Logan Paul but gets Santos Escobar instead. Knight and Escobar get into a brawl. Knight takes out Escobar with the BFT and then gets attacked by Logan Paul.

Triple Threat Qualifier set for next week between LA Knight, Santos Escobar and Logan Paul

